request.description:
Returns a single logistics assignment with all references fully populated.

## Populated Fields:
- **enquiryId** — Full enquiry record including:
  - **fieldOwnerId** → { firstName, lastName, mobileNo, role }
  - **assignedSelectorId** → { firstName, lastName, mobileNo, role }
- **companyId** — Full company record (companyName, legalName, taxId, headquarters)
- **munshiId** → { firstName, lastName, mobileNo }
- **driverId** → { firstName, lastName, mobileNo, vehicleId: { vehicleNumber, vehicleType } }
- **vehicleId** — Full vehicle record (vehicleNumber, vehicleType, isActive)

## Access:
Restricted to Admin and Operational Manager roles only.

